- API layer on top of Excalibur 2D canvas and Three.js 3D canvas
- Graph based game editor
- AI based input for scene/image/narrative generation
- Bundle and run on any device
- Test/Debug and Run instantly on phone or browser
- CSS theme styling
- Framework for designing custom game rulesets
- Execute custom ruleset

Phase 1

- Design core UI, cyber themed
- Design initial game location block
    - Includes image header, description and various actions, movement cells
    - URL for image should connect to ComfyUI flow that generates an image
    - Block can save image internally
    - Can type description of what you want and block calls AI endpoint to generate imeage
